import React from "react";
import { ACTIONS } from "./App";

export default function DigitButton({ dispatch, digit }) {
	return (
		<>
			<button className="span-two">AC</button>
			<button>DEL</button>
			<button>รท</button>

			<button>1</button>
			<button>2</button>
			<button>3</button>
			<button>*</button>

			<button>4</button>
			<button>5</button>
			<button>6</button>
			<button>+</button>

			<button>7</button>
			<button>8</button>
			<button>9</button>
			<button>-</button>

			<button>.</button>
			<button>0</button>
			<button className="span-two">=</button>
		</>
	);
}
